     The sign for "mistake" also means "wrong" and it has a couple of variations.
    </p>
    <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
     <br/>
     MISTAKE / inaccurate / "be wrong" / "an error"
     <br/>
