     <br/>
    </p>
    <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
    <p>
     <br/>
     Sample sentence:
     <br/>
     How many errors did you get on the last (previous) test you took in this 
	class?
     <br/>
     = PAST TEST THIS CLASS YOU WRONG how-MANY?
     <br/>
     <br/>
    </p>
